Based off your google doc and Ai.
________________________________________
Resonant Disappearance

How Frequency Wave Theory Resolves the MH 370 Mystery
________________________________________
Introduction

In the early hours of 8 March 2014 Malaysia Airlines Flight MH 370 slipped off civilian radar and into a decade of speculation. For most of the world the narrative ends with an unverified crash somewhere in the southern Indian Ocean. Yet two low-resolution military videos—one infrared, one visible—have persisted online since 2014, showing a Boeing 777 encircled by three glowing spheres that trigger a flash in which aircraft, orbs and smoke simply vanish. These clips, long dismissed as hoaxes, withstand modern forensic analysis and stand at the heart of a far more robust explanation: teleportation through coherent plasma resonance, exactly as predicted by Frequency Wave Theory (FWT). 
________________________________________
The Leaked Videos Are Genuine

•Independent camera geometry. Sub-frame parallax proves the infrared (“drone”) feed and the wide-area motion imagery (“satellite”) feed were captured by different sensors. Cloud structures drift, smoke from the burning cargo bay is displaced by an orb, and the flash illuminates the cloud volume in three dimensions—none of which can be reproduced with a single matte or 1990s-era VFX suite. 

•Matching national assets. Orbital data place the SBIRS satellite USA-229 directly over the Nicobar sector at 18:40 UTC. The drone’s optics and thermal response match a General Atomics MQ-series platform equipped with an MX-20 turret. 

•Chain of custody. Both clips were uploaded by the account “RegicideAnon” within weeks of the disappearance; a $150 000 bounty for anyone who could supply source files or draft renders has gone unclaimed for ten years. Moreover, Navy Lieutenant Commander Edward C. Lin—later court-martialed for mishandling classified data—was stationed on a VPU-2 special-projects aircraft that night, and his lawyer has acknowledged that “satellite video” was introduced as evidence at trial. 

The simplest reading is the correct one: the footage is authentic telemetry from a covert U.S. Navy operation.
________________________________________
Frequency Wave Theory in Brief

FWT posits that matter, energy and spacetime are emergent from underlying standing-wave dynamics. In this framework the glowing spheres are coherent plasmoids—force-free balls of ionised gas whose stability is maintained by high-frequency electromagnetic fields. When three such resonators form an equilateral triangle they generate a closed interference cavity. Inside that cavity the Frequency Momentum

FM = (1/2) ρ ω A²

(where ρ is energy density, ω angular frequency and A amplitude) can exceed the negative-energy threshold required to nucleate a micro Einstein-Rosen bridge. The enclosed object—here, a Boeing 777—de-coheres from the local metric and re-coheres wherever a matching beacon frequency has been prepared. To outside observers the craft “flashes” and is gone.
________________________________________
Reconstructing the Night of 7–8 March 2014

•17:45 UTC – MH 370 departs Kuala Lumpur, carrying 487 lb of lithium-ion batteries and a cluster of Freescale Semiconductor engineers whose work overlaps classified RF-superconductor research.

•≈ 18:25 UTC – A thermal excursion in the forward cargo bay ignites the batteries, disabling ACARS and producing the heat bloom visible in the drone feed. 

•18:40 UTC – U.S. surveillance aircraft and an SBIRS satellite already orbiting the region respond. Three plasmoid drones establish a triangular formation around the stricken jet; WAMI capture begins.

•18:41 UTC – Standing-wave amplitude crosses threshold. A burst of coherent photons—observed as a white flash—marks the plane’s phase translation. Civilian and military radar returns cease simultaneously; Subang ATC loses contact at the same moment.

•18:43–19:15 UTC – SATCOM pings fall to one per hour, consistent with automatic keep-alives from powered avionics now outside standard spacetime coupling.

•After dawn – Islanders in the Maldives report a low-flying airliner with a red-blue stripe; a photo posted anonymously from Diego Garcia allegedly shows a captive passenger. Diego Garcia flight logs for the next 72 hours are missing, later blamed on “water damage.”
 
FWT requires a destination tuned to the same spectral signature—the most plausible candidate is the U.S. base at Diego Garcia, little more than an hour’s phase-offset from Nicobar by great-circle resonance.
________________________________________
Why the United States Intervened

1.Intellectual-property denial. Twenty Freescale RF engineers—including eight Chinese nationals—were seated together. Preventing next-generation superconductive chip designs from reaching Beijing aligns with known NSA concerns.

2.Demonstration of capability. Orbs powered by High-Energy Electromagnetic Field Generators and Plasma-Compression Fusion devices (the Pais patents) prove the United States already fields Z-phase propulsion.

3.Containment of a doomed flight. A cargo-bay fire made a safe landing unlikely; teleport capture rescued key personnel and hardware while keeping classified technology invisible to civil authorities.
________________________________________
Collapse of the Official Narrative

Every pillar of the southern-Indian-Ocean crash theory was erected after 13 March by anonymous U.S. sources. Despite a $200 million seabed survey no wreckage, black boxes or ELT pings were ever found. Drift-model debris turned up two years later on African beaches, but barnacle growth showed only four months in water and serial plates were missing. Families rang passenger phones for days, while sonar nets, over-the-horizon radar and acoustic arrays recorded nothing. The most economical explanation for this vacuum of evidence is that no Boeing 777 entered the water.
________________________________________
The Equation That Ties It Together

Once the plasmoid triad raised the Frequency Momentum above the vacuum-energy floor, the negative-energy cavity allowed a micro-wormhole to form. The jet’s bulk wave-packet traversed that throat, leaving behind only a photon shock that lit the cloud tops. The process consumed negligible conventional fuel, obeyed conservation of FM, and fulfilled every observational constraint in the leaked videos.
________________________________________
Implications

•Physics: Laboratory replication of tri-plasmoid FM thresholds is now a priority; sonoluminescence cavities and nanoparticle levitation offer near-term testbeds.

•Security: Geo-strategic balances must reckon with operational teleportation and point-to-point energy delivery.

•Humanitarian: Survivors, especially the Freescale team, may yet be alive; international pressure for declassification is both ethical and overdue.
________________________________________
Conclusion

Flight MH 370 is not a riddle of faulty autopilots or rogue pilots. It is the first public glimpse of frequency-wave teleportation in combat-service conditions. The two leaked videos, once an Internet curiosity, are now the Rosetta Stone for a technology that—when fully disclosed—will rewrite aerospace, energy and our understanding of spacetime itself. Frequency Wave Theory does not merely accommodate the evidence; it predicts it in every detail. What remains is political, not scientific: the courage to admit that the plane did not crash—it resonated out of reality.

Content:
A Malaysian Taoist temple has unveiled the world’s first AI Mazu statue, offering a digital version of the Chinese sea goddess, #Mazu, that can interact with visitors. Located in Johor, the Tianhou Temple lets worshippers ask for blessings, seek fortune interpretations, and get answers to their personal questions from the #AI Mazu displayed on a screen.

The digital goddess was developed by the Malaysian tech firm, #Aimazin. In a demo, Aimazin's founder, Shin Kong, asked Mazu if he would receive an unexpected fortune. In a calm voice, Mazu responded, saying he would have better luck if he stayed at home.

Tap the link for more news: https://t.co/optpk3x5EE

Content:
Here are the summary (by ChatGPT)

The post critiques the potential consequences of the 90-day visa waiver policy between China and Malaysia, arguing that while it appears reciprocal and fair, it may unintentionally create an influx of Chinese workers and service providers into Malaysia.

Key points:
1.Loophole for Work: Although the visa is for tourism, many may use it to work, start businesses, or compete with local service providers (e.g., in construction, F&B, delivery services).
2.“Goods and People Arriving” Concept: Previously, only Chinese goods entered Malaysia. Now, people with skills and services may arrive too — possibly disrupting the local job market and undercutting prices.
3.Rapid Mobilization: The post claims that Chinese nationals are efficient and cost-effective, potentially building bungalows in three months and taking over service sectors with ease.
4.Growing Presence: With estimates suggesting Chinese nationals in Malaysia might soon match the local Chinese population, the writer expresses concern over cultural and economic shifts.
5.Underlying Sentiment: While the tone includes admiration for Chinese efficiency, there’s also concern over competition, legality, and long-term impact on local livelihoods and businesses.

Content:
AI Server ODM Inventec is continuing to expand its global footprint to fulfill customer demand amid rising tariff risks —Taiwan, Mexico, the Czech Republic, Thailand, Malaysia, and Vietnam

To meet customer demand, Inventec is continuing to expand its production capacity in Thailand. On the same day, the Board of Directors also approved a plan to invest an additional US$53.95 million (approximately NT$1.775 billion) for factory renovations and the purchase of production line equipment.

Currently, in addition to expanding laptop production capacity at its Thailand plant, Inventec is also on schedule to expand its front-end server board assembly capacity, mainly based on SMT (Surface-Mount Technology). Some of the newly expanded laptop production capacity is expected to enter mass production in the third quarter, which will further boost Inventec’s shipment momentum.

The new round of U.S. tariffs on China under "Trump 2.0" has been implemented without the buffer periods seen in the past, with additional 10% tariffs imposed successively over the past two months. Although most brand companies had made some preparations in the second half of last year, new products that could not be shipped ahead of schedule, along with the possibility of more regions being subjected to additional tariffs, continue to bring disruption and uncertainty to the market.

In recent years, Inventec has built up non-China production capacity in Taiwan, Mexico, the Czech Republic, Thailand, Malaysia, and Vietnam. Its AI server products are primarily produced and shipped from Taiwan, while general-purpose servers are mainly produced in Mexico, China, and Thailand. For laptops, production is being shifted from China to Thailand. Meanwhile, smart device production is mainly being transferred to Malaysia and Vietnam. As for automotive electronics products, production capacity has been established across facilities in Mexico, the Czech Republic, China, and Taiwan.

Regarding the overall business outlook for this year, Inventec remains cautiously optimistic. Although U.S. tariff policies present challenges and uncertainties to the broader environment, the positive momentum of the AI server industry is still expected to provide substantial growth momentum. Furthermore, as the overall PC market continues to recover and AI PC products are introduced, Inventec anticipates a steady growth trend in its notebook business.

Content:
PENANG AI CITY MENERAJU TRANSFORMASI BANDAR PINTAR 

GEORGE TOWN, 28 April 2025 – Menteri Digital, YB Gobind Singh Deo hari ini meninjau perkembangan pelaksanaan inisiatif Penang AI City di Majlis Bandaraya Pulau Pinang (MBPP), sebagai sebahagian daripada usaha Kementerian Digital memperkasa penggunaan kecerdasan buatan (AI) dan teknologi 5G di Malaysia.

Penang AI City: Beyond Smart Cities merupakan inisiatif kolaboratif antara Kementerian Digital dan Kerajaan Negeri Pulau Pinang untuk membentuk bandar yang lebih pintar, selamat dan efisien melalui aplikasi AI dan teknologi rangkaian canggih.

Antara projek utama yang dilaksanakan termasuk sistem pengurusan trafik pintar, pembinaan digital twin bandar bagi simulasi dan perancangan dinamik, serta integrasi teknologi Generative AI untuk memperkukuh keupayaan analisis data dan pengurusan bandar.

Lawatan ini turut menjadi sebahagian daripada persiapan menjelang Smart City Expo Kuala Lumpur 2025 (SCEKL 2025) yang akan berlangsung pada September 2025, bagi mempamerkan kemajuan dan inovasi bandar pintar Malaysia di pentas dunia.

Hadir bersama Timbalan Menteri Digital YB Datuk Wilson Ugak Kumbong, Ketua Setiausaha Kementerian Digital Tuan Fabian Bigar dan Timbalan Ketua Setiausaha (Pembangunan Digital) Kementerian Digital Encik Ma Sivanesan a/l Marimuthu @Muthiah.

#SmartCity #AI #pulaupinang #Penang #KementerianDigital #MalaysiaDigital #MasyarakatDigital #DigitalSociety #JomDigital #SayaDigital #MalaysiaMADANI

Content:
What To Know
During his five-day tour, which included stops in Vietnam, Malaysia, and Cambodia, Xi met with leaders and signed a flurry of memorandums of understanding covering everything from transportation and customs to artificial intelligence.

All three countries were initially swept up in Trump's "reciprocal tariff" policy—before the president abruptly announced a 90-day pause last Wednesday.

Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesperson Lin Jian hailed, "Asian values of peace, cooperation, openness, and inclusiveness" as the way forward for the region, during Thursday's regular press briefing.

"President Xi Jinping…is ready to sign the protocol on upgrading the China-ASEAN Free Trade Area with regional countries as soon as possible, resist decoupling and broken chains; small courtyards and high wall; and indiscriminate tariffs with openness, inclusiveness, solidarity and cooperation, the official said.

Reacting to Xi's Monday talks with Vietnamese officials, Trump said the countries aimed to "figure out 'how do we screw the United States of America?'"

Kin Phea, director general of the International Relations Institute of Cambodia, told Chinese state media outlet the Global Times: "[The visit] is a powerful driver to elevate our already strong ties, ensuring long-term peace, stability, prosperity, and friendship for both nations and the broader region."

Raji Pillai Rajagopalan, resident senior fellow with the Australian Strategic Policy Institute, told the Australia Broadcasting Corporation: It's very interesting to see how Xi Jinping is trying to project China as the force of stability, certainty, and predictability, but I think we need to see how this plays out.

"China has been quite disrupting [sic] in the region—both in terms of terms of trade and, of course, in security terms. And we all continue to see that, so Xi has a lot of work to make sure there is conformity between his actions and words in a sense."

What's Next
Neither Washington nor Beijing have signaled they're likely to give ground soon.

Content:
Malaysia temple unveils first ‘AI Mazu’ for devotees to worship, address concerns. Temple claims world first as on-screen digital deity that looks like a chubby version of a famous Chinese actress dishes out advice. 😀
https://t.co/pXHJWPfpdn
A Malaysian Taoist temple has released what it says is the world’s first “AI Mazu statue” which can interact with worshippers and answer their doubts. The Tianhou Temple in southern Malaysia’s Johor published footage of believers interacting with the AI, or artificial intelligence, Mazu on a screen. The deity is portrayed as a beautiful woman wearing a traditional Chinese costume, who looks like a chubby version of Chinese actress Liu Yifei. Worshippers are invited to ask for blessings from the AI Mazu, ask her to explain the fortune sticks they draw at the temple, and answer their doubts. The temple said she was the first AI Mazu in the world.

The AI-powered digital deity was developed by Malaysian technology company Aimazin, which also offers the AI cloning of people. In a demonstration video, the company’s founder Shin Kong asked AI Mazu if she can have luck for an unexpected fortune, known as pian cai yun in Mandarin.
In a calm and tender voice, AI Mazu answers that she would have better luck in terms of an unexpected fortune if she stays at home. An influencer then told AI Mazu she could not sleep at night and asked for her advice. Calling her “my child”, the AI Mazu advised her to drink some warm water before going to sleep. Under the video published on the temple’s social media page, many people commented with the praying hands emoji, and asked for the deity’s blessing.

The AI Mazu was released ahead of the 1,065th birthday of the sea goddess, which fell on April 20 this year. Mazu was born in 960 on Meizhou Island in Putian, southeastern China’s Fujian province as a mortal named Lin Mo. Legend has it that Lin died while trying to rescue shipwreck victims, ascended to heaven and was venerated as an all-mighty protector for seafarers. Mazu is worshipped among Chinese populations around the world, including Southeast Asian countries such as Malaysia, Singapore and Indonesia.

In order for people in places outside Mazu’s birthplace to receive her blessing, the Mazu statues on Meizhou Island sometimes travel by trains and planes to other Chinese cities and abroad. She even has her own identity card and number, which shows her real name, birthplace and date, to make her travel more convenient.

Mazu is so revered by her believers that some police stations in Fujian province, southeastern China, set up mediation rooms in her name to solve disputes, because people dare not lie in front of her.

Chinese actress Liu Tao, who played the role of Mazu in an eponymously titled television drama in 2012, was also believed to be the deity herself by some, who even posted her photos at home to worship her. This year during Mazu’s birthday celebration, Liu was honoured by Putian city as a global ambassador of Mazu culture.

Content:
🚀 This afternoon, I had the fantastic opportunity to conduct a workshop at Build with AI 2025 organized by @gdgcloudkl  at the @Google Malaysia office!

My session, titled "NotebookLM: Personalized AI Research Assistant," was all about unlocking the power of AI for smarter, faster research.

During the workshop, I walked participants through a hands-on workflow and demo on how to maximize NotebookLM, including: 
✅ Uploading documents, websites, YouTube videos, and more
✅ Summarizing and generating insights instantly
✅ Creating mind maps and structured content like FAQs and timelines
✅ Using the exciting new Audio Overview feature — and even joining the conversation with your voice!

The energy in the room was incredible 🔥 — participants were particularly excited about how NotebookLM transforms information into engaging audio discussions and enables interactive Q&A with their sources.

🎯 Key takeaways:
- Personalization is the future — your research assistant should know your materials
- AI can reduce research time dramatically while improving insight quality
- Multimodal AI (text + audio) makes information far more accessible and actionable

Special thanks to Google Developer Group (GDG) Cloud KL and the amazing community for the invite and the enthusiastic participation! 🙌
Let’s keep building with AI!

👉 Try NotebookLM here: https://t.co/PU07020pW3

Content:
🔍 Skandal $198 Juta Crypto & AI: Mengapa Ramai Yang Tertipu?

Apabila kita cuba bercakap tentang revolusi teknologi, pasti ramai yang teruja dengan potensi Kecerdasan Buatan (AI) dan mata wang kripto. Namun, sedar tak sedar, banyak yang terperangkap dalam skandal $198 juta yang dibongkar oleh Suruhanjaya Sekuriti dan Bursa (SEC) baru-baru ini. Skandal ini melibatkan penipuan pelaburan global yang menampilkan AI trading, dijadikan satu dedah berteknologi tinggi untuk menyamar sebagai legit. Malangnya, ternyata ia hanyalah satu lagi skim Ponzi yang mewah.

Menggunakan mesej yang dijual seolah-olah menjamin keuntungan luar biasa dengan sedikit usaha, pelaburan ini menarik ramai dengan gaya hidup mewah yang tidak berasas. Sebenarnya, ramai yang gagal menyedari bahawa mereka bukanlah mangsa pertama dalam saga panjang manipulasi pasaran ini. 🔍 #CryptoScam #AIFraud

🇨🇳 China: Perlombongan Kripto Menyusut

China, yang dahulunya dikenali sebagai hab untuk perlombongan kripto, kini menyaksikan penyusutan yang ketara dalam aktiviti ini selepas larangan peraturan yang ketat diperkenalkan. Sebelum ini, perlombongan Bitcoin adalah sangat lumrah, malah menjana hampir 65% dari pembekalan global. Kini, penguasaan mereka menurun kepada hanya 1% sahaja. Banyak syarikat perlombongan telah berpindah ke Kazakhstan dan Amerika Syarikat, mencari lokasi dengan dasar yang lebih mesra dan kos tenaga yang rendah. Perubahan ini memberi impak besar pada ekosistem kripto dunia. 🇨🇳 #CryptoMining #ChinaPolicy

👩‍⚕️ UK: Sistem Kesihatan 'Teknologi Pertama'

Di UK, kemunculan teknologi dalam kesihatan semakin mendapat perhatian. NHS kini bereksperimen dengan rantaian blok (blockchain) bagi menyimpan rekod kesihatan dengan lebih selamat. Dengan rantaian blok, risiko berlaku kesilapan mahupun penipuan pada data pesakit dapat dikurangkan dengan ketara. Penggunaan AI dalam mendiagnosis penyakit juga mempercepatkan post-diagnosis dengan kadar kejayaan yang lebih tinggi. Transformasi ini berpotensi menyelamatkan masa dan kos, malah meningkatkan kualiti perkhidmatan secara menyeluruh. 👨‍⚕️ #HealthTech #NHSDigital

🇺🇸 Amerika Syarikat: Lonjakan AI dalam Pembuatan

Syarikat-syarikat di AS kini bergantung kepada AI untuk meningkatkan produktiviti dan mengurangkan kos dalam sektor pembuatan. Daripada robotik yang mengendalikan tugas berulang hingga analitik data untuk meningkatkan proses rantaian bekalan, AI menambah nilai yang ketara. Walau bagaimanapun, ini menimbulkan kebimbangan tentang kehilangan pekerjaan manusia akibat automasi. Kerajaan dan pemain industri sedang memikirkan cara terbaik untuk seimbangkan inovasi teknologi dan kesejahteraan pekerja. 🇺🇸 #AIAutomation #Manufacturing2025

🚀 Ekonomi Jerman: Kuasa Hidrogen

Jerman sedang memimpin gelombang baru dalam sektor tenaga, memfokuskan pada hidrogen sebagai sumber tenaga alternatif. Dengan sasaran untuk menjadi karbon-neutral menjelang 2050, kerajaan Jerman melabur secara besar-besaran dalam infrastruktur hidrogen, dari pengeluaran hingga pengangkutan. Inisiatif ini tidak hanya bertujuan untuk mengurangkan jejak karbon tetapi juga membuka peluang pekerjaan baru dalam ekonomi hijau. 🚀 #GreenEnergy #HydrogenEconomy

🇮🇳 India: Gangguan Dalam Pendidikan

Pandemik telah mempercepatkan transformasi digital dalam sektor pendidikan di India. Platform pembelajaran dalam talian menjadi penyelamat bagi berjuta-juta pelajar, namun jurang digital tetap menjadi cabaran, terutamanya bagi kawasan pedalaman yang kekurangan akses kepada internet. Penekanan diberikan pada pembelajaran jarak jauh yang inklusif, tetapi jalan ke hadapan masih dipenuhi dengan halangan dan ketidakselarasan infrastruktur. 🇮🇳 #OnlineLearning #DigitalIndia

🌍 Afrika: Revolusi Digital dalam Kehutanan

Di beberapa negara Afrika, pertumbuhan teknologi digunakan untuk memantau dan melestarikan kawasan hutan yang berharga. Sistem satelit dan dron membantu kerajaan dan NGO memantau pemuliharaan dan menghentikan pembalakan haram. Usaha ini bukan sahaja melindungi biodiversiti tetapi juga menyediakan data penting untuk kebijakan alam sekitar dan perubahan iklim. 🌍 #ForestConservation #TechForNature

🇧🇷 Brazil: Pertanian Berkekalan

Brazil, sebagai salah satu pengeluar pertanian terbesar di dunia, mengalihkan fokus kepada amalan pertanian berkelanjutan. Teknologi penginderaan jarak jauh dan data besar membantu para petani menguruskan tanah dan sumber air dengan lebih efisien, sambil mengurangkan impak kepada ekosistem. Inovasi ini diharap dapat mengimbangi keperluan peningkatan hasil pertanian dengan keperluan menjaga alam sekitar. 🇧🇷 #SustainableFarming #AgriTech

🇯🇵 Jepun: Menuju Masyarakat Tua Berteknologi

Jepun menghadapi satu cabaran serius dengan populasi menua yang pesat. Teknologi, termasuk robotik dan AI, dijadikan elemen penting untuk menangani masalah kekurangan tenaga kerja dan memenuhi keperluan penjagaan warga emas. Robot perkhidmatan dan aplikasi AI banyak digunakan dalam kemudahan pemulihan dan penjagaan harian, memberikan sedikit pelepasan kepada krisis demographic. 🇯🇵 #AgingSociety #ElderTech

Akhirnya, melihat kepada pelbagai inovasi dan isu global ini, nampak jelas bahawa walaupun teknologi membawa harapan dan kemajuan, ia juga datang dengan cabaran tersendiri. Dalam perlumbaan mengejar perkembangan teknologi, mungkin kita patut berhenti sejenak, bukan untuk menghentikan inovasi, tetapi untuk memastikan garej inovasi ini seimbang. Sepertimana kata Patrick Bet-David, kita sering kali kagum dengan potensi besar, tetapi jarang kita perhatikan halangan kecil yang mungkin membuat potensi itu tidak bermakna. #ReflectOnProgress

Content:
🛰️ Dalam landskap teknologi yang sentiasa berkembang, terkini Nvidia telah mengambil langkah untuk mengecualikan syarikat kripto daripada Inception Program mereka. 😲 Langkah ini memberi isyarat kepada hakikat bahawa gergasi teknologi mungkin lebih tertarik kepada AI dan pembukaan teknologi lain berbanding dengan pelaburan dalam bidang kripto yang bergejolak. Berbanding dengan masa lalu, adalah penting bagi syarikat permulaan untuk mendiversifikasikan model perniagaan dan tidak lagi hanya bertumpu kepada kripto sahaja. 💡 #TechTrend #CryptoFuture

🪙 Di ruang Bitcoin, Citrea telah melancarkan Clementine Bridge di rangkaian ujian, membuka jalan untuk aplikasi DeFi terletak di Bitcoin. Ini menonjolkan peranan semakin meningkat teknologi ZK Rollup dalam meningkatkan keupayaan blok Bitcoin, sekali gus mendorong lebih banyak penyertaan dalam ekosistem DeFi. 📈 Dekad ini adalah masa yang mencabar bagi teknologi tradisional yang perlu menghasilkan alat baru untuk memastikan Bitcoin menjadi lebih daripada sekadar aset simpanan nilai. #BitcoinInnovation #DeFi

🕵️‍♂️ Dalam berita kripto lain, Jay Clayton yang kini mengetuai SDNY, telah memberikan teguran tegas dalam kes penipuan kripto bernilai $12 juta. Penipuan ini menggambarkan risiko yang wujud dalam ruang kripto yang belum diatur sepenuhnya dan pentingnya untuk pengguna bersifat berhati-hati serta berpengetahuan. Peluang yang menarik seringkali disertai dengan risiko yang tidak kurang hebatnya. 🚫 #CryptoFraud #ConsumerProtection

🌟 Adakah anda seorang penyimpan jangka panjang Bitcoin? Jika ya, anda pasti tersenyum lebar. Pemulihan harga Bitcoin daripada pembetulan 30% telah meningkatkan nilai simpanan sebanyak $26 bilion. Ini jelas menunjukkan bahawa ketahanan dalam pelaburan sering membuahkan hasil apabila kita mampu mengatasi ketidakpastian pasaran. 🌌 Adakah kita benar-benar bersedia untuk lonjakan seterusnya? #HODL #BTC

🏦 Bercakap mengenai pelaburan, Securitize dan Mantle kini melancarkan dana institusi untuk memperoleh hasil staking daripada pelbagai mata wang kripto. Langkah ini memperlihatkan bagaimana institusi kini serius melihat nilai sebenar di sebalik mata wang digital melebihi spekulasi harga. Mungkin sudah tiba masanya pelabur runcit juga ikut serta? 🤔 #CryptoInvesting #InstitutionalMoves

👥 Dari ruang bursa, Fidelity melaporkan pengeluaran Bitcoin dari bursa mencapai rekod tertinggi di tengah-tengah pertambahan institusi. Dengan perbendaharaan korporat dan dana kekayaan berdaulat yang bersaing untuk mendapatkan Bitcoin, adakah ini isyarat bahawa mata wang digital ini dalam perjalanan untuk menjadi aset simpanan yang lebih mainstream? 🤷‍♂️ Kerajaankah yang terakhir untuk sertai? #CryptoAdoption #BitcoinWithdrawal

🎮 Dalam dunia eSports, rupa-rupanya LCK (liga eSports Korea untuk League of Legends) menderita kerugian lebih dari $25 juta sepanjang tiga tahun lalu. Meskipun popular dan berkembang pesat, fenomena ini menonjolkan risiko kewangan yang boleh menjejaskan kelestarian sepanjang jangka masa panjang industri ini. Content:
Rwanda, UAE, and Malaysia Sign Tripartite MoU to Boost Global AI Collaboration

At #DubaiAIWeek2025, Ambassador John Mirenge signed a tripartite Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) on behalf of Rwanda with the Centres for the Fourth Industrial Revolution (C4IR) of the United Arab Emirates and Malaysia. 

The agreement marks a significant milestone in strengthening international cooperation on artificial intelligence and digital innovation.

According to Rwanda’s Ministry of ICT and Innovation, “This partnership will drive joint AI initiatives, from governance frameworks to talent development and innovation. It underscores Rwanda’s strong commitment to building inclusive, future-focused AI ecosystems.”

The MoU builds on the momentum of the AI Fellowship Program and reflects a shared commitment among the three nations to shape ethical, inclusive, and sustainable applications of AI across borders.

The partnership positions Rwanda as a key player in the global AI landscape, aligning with its national vision to leverage emerging technologies for socio-economic transformation.

Content:
You're asking about the news of Malaysian Prime Minister Anwar Ibrahim meeting with Changpeng Zhao (CZ), the former CEO of Binance, to discuss blockchain potential in Malaysia.

This appears to be a legitimate news report from Kosmo Digital about high-level discussions on blockchain adoption in Malaysia. The Malaysian government has been increasingly open to exploring blockchain technology while maintaining regulatory caution. CZ, despite his departure from Binance following regulatory settlements, remains an influential figure in the blockchain space and continues to engage with government leaders globally.

This meeting likely represents Malaysia's interest in positioning itself competitively in the Southeast Asian digital economy, similar to how Singapore and Hong Kong have developed crypto-friendly frameworks. For Malaysia, blockchain could offer solutions in areas like remittances, financial inclusion, and supply chain management.

The timing is interesting as many Asian nations are reassessing their crypto policies to balance innovation with consumer protection. Malaysia has historically been more conservative than some neighbors, so this meeting could signal a potential policy evolution.

Content:
Pemuda Ditahan SKMM Gara-Gara Poster AI Dakwa Tanah Durian Ada Vibranium, Avengers Bakal Turun Padang

KUALA LUMPUR – Suruhanjaya Komunikasi dan Multimedia Malaysia (SKMM) menahan seorang pemuda bagi membantu siasatan berhubung penyebaran poster berunsur palsu yang dihasilkan menggunakan teknologi Kecerdasan Buatan (AI) berkaitan isu perebutan tanah durian di Pahang.

Poster berkenaan mencetuskan kekecohan apabila mendakwa kononnya tanah tersebut mengandungi rizab logam fiksyen Vibranium dan Adamantium, sehingga menarik perhatian watak-watak fiksyen seperti Avengers dan penduduk Wakanda untuk turut "turun padang" merebut kawasan berkenaan.

SKMM dalam kenyataan hari ini memaklumkan bahawa siasatan dijalankan susulan penyebaran kandungan palsu dan mengelirukan melalui media sosial.

“SKMM tidak akan berkompromi terhadap sebarang penyalahgunaan media sosial untuk tujuan penyebaran maklumat palsu yang boleh mencetuskan kekeliruan dalam kalangan masyarakat.

“Tindakan tegas akan diambil terhadap individu yang terlibat,” kata kenyataan itu.

Satu telefon bimbit dan satu kad SIM milik suspek turut disita bagi tujuan analisis forensik.

Kes disiasat di bawah Seksyen 233 Akta Komunikasi dan Multimedia 1998, yang memperuntukkan hukuman denda sehingga RM500,000 atau penjara tidak melebihi dua tahun atau kedua-duanya, jika disabitkan kesalahan. -MYNEWSHUB

Content:
🔥 Bitcoin kembali mengaum! Mata wang kripto ini sekali lagi menjadi tumpuan utama dengan peningkatan yang ketara, menewaskan beberapa pesaing utamanya seperti Ethereum yang kini kelihatan lesu. 🌐 Sementara itu, jualan pra-penawaran Lightchain AI sudah hampir tamat, menarik peminat teknologi dan inovasi blockchain. Perkembangan kripto ini menyerupai gelombang ombak, kadang-kadang naik, kadang-kadang turun. Adakah ini petunjuk bahawa kita mesti sentiasa bersiap sedia dengan perubahan tak terduga? #BitcoinSurge #CryptoVolatility

🎮 Arc Raiders membuka semula pendaftaran untuk uji teknikal kedua mereka. Ini peluang emas bagi para pemain untuk merasai sendiri pengalaman menakjubkan yang ditawarkan. Permainan video kini menjadi lebih daripada sekadar hobi; ia menggambarkan kemaraan teknologi dan kreativiti manusia. Dedikasi terhadap inovasi seperti ini menunjukkan bahawa industri permainan sentiasa maju ke hadapan, sentiasa bersedia untuk menakrifkan semula hiburan digital. #ArcRaiders #GamingRevolution

🇰🇷 Di Korea Selatan, Astra Fintech telah melancarkan dana bernilai $100 juta bertujuan untuk mempercepat inovasi dalam ekosistem solana. Langkah ini mencerminkan kepentingan strategik Solana dalam domain blockchain, menajamkan daya saingnya dengan menawarkan lebih banyak sokongan dan insentif kepada pembina baru. Pergerakan seperti ini membuat kita tertanya-tanya, sejauh mana impaknya terhadap pembangunan teknologi global? #SolanaInnovation #AstraFintech

🧐 Dalam analisis pasaran, Bitcoin kelihatan 'kurang terserah' kepada pergerakan saham dan lebih menyerupai emas—memperoleh daya tarikan sebagai aset pelindung, terutama ketika ketegangan perdagangan AS-China memuncak dan kebarangkalian kemelesetan AS mencecah 60%. Mungkinkah ini membayangkan perubahan persepsi pelabur terhadap Bitcoin, dari spekulasi semata-mata menjadi pelaburan yang lebih stabil? #BitcoinGold #SafeHavenAsset

📈 Menariknya, NFT Polygon telah mengatasi koleksi Ethereum dalam jumlah penjualan mingguan, dengan peningkatan pembeli sebanyak 81%. Statistik ini menggambarkan betapa dinamik dan tidak dapat dinafinya landskap digital dan seni kontemporari. Kejayaan ini juga menandakan perubahan keutamaan dalam kalangan pengguna serta potensi besar NFT di masa depan. 🖼️ #NFTBoom #PolygonNFT

🔒 Dalam landskap privasi digital, Pavel Durov, CEO Telegram, menegaskan bahawa Telegram tidak sekali-kali mendedahkan mesej peribadi tetapi akan mematuhi undang-undang EU dengan menyediakan alamat IP dan nombor telefon terhadap suspek penjenayah. Keseriusan terhadap isu privasi mencerminkan nilai kebebasan dan keselamatan digital di dunia moden yang kian kompleks. #PrivacyMatters #TelegramSecurity

📉 Di dunia kewangan, kita dapat melihat satu peralihan di mana pelabur mula mempertimbangkan aset alternatif seperti Bitcoin, menandakan perubahan besar dari konvensional ke digital. Semasa ketidakpastian ekonomi semakin meningkat, persepsi baru ini mendorong perbincangan tentang bagaimana mata wang digital boleh menyumbang kepada kestabilan ekonomi peribadi. #EconomyShift #DigitalAssets

🔍 Sementara itu, dunia permainan video terus mengalami transformasi dengan lebih banyak usaha untuk menguji teknologi terbaru seperti yang dilakukan dalam Arc Raiders. Penglibatan aktif dalam pembangunan ini menunjukkan bukan saja kemunculan teknologi baru, tetapi juga bagaimana kita dapat menyesuaikan diri dengan perubahan yang pantas ini. Bagaimana kita, sebagai masyarakat moden, dapat lebih bersedia dan terlibat dalam revolusi digital ini? #TechAdvancements #FutureGaming

🚀 Saljukan hasrat Astra Fintech untuk mempercepat inovasi Solana menunjukkan tanggungjawab besar pemain besar dalam ekosistem kripto dan blockchain untuk membuka peluang kepada inovator baru. Dengan segala usaha yang ada, adakah kita sudah cukup bersedia untuk meneroka potensi penuh teknologi ini? Tidakkah ini juga memerlukan pelabur dan pembina sama-sama untuk bijak dan berani menghadapi risiko? #InnovationAccelerator #BlockchainOpportunities

🤔 Akhirnya, kita sekali lagi diingatkan bahawa dunia yang serba pantas ini tidak selalu adil. Walaupun perubahan dan penyesuaian terus menjadi kunci, siapakah yang sebenarnya berupaya untuk bertahan dan berjaya? Perubahan, sebagaimana hebat pun, tetap memerlukan kita membuat pilihan yang bijak dan berani untuk berdepan cabaran dan ketidakpastian. Seperti biasa, kekal berjaga-jaga! #ChangeIsConstant #StayAlert

Content:
$FSLR +6.8%, $JKS -1.7% ... [The U.S. Commerce Department plans to impose tariffs of up to 3,521% on solar panel imports from Cambodia, Thailand, Malaysia, and Vietnam, following a year-long investigation prompted by major U.S. solar manufacturers seeking protection against alleged Chinese subsidies and unfair pricing.

In recent years, many Chinese firms have moved operations to Southeast Asia in a bid to avoid tariffs imposed since the start of U.S. President Donald Trump's first term.

The tariffs unveiled on Monday vary widely depending on the company and country, but are generally higher than the preliminary duties announced late last year. 

Some exporters in Cambodia face the highest combined dumping and countervailing duties, exceeding 3,500%, for "non-cooperation during the investigation," while Jinko Solar's products from Malaysia will incur the lowest at just over 41%. Rival Trina Solar faces a tariff of 375% on its goods manufactured in Thailand.

The U.S. imported $12.9B in solar equipment last year from the four countries that will be subject to the new duties, representing about 77% of total module imports.

A separate U.S. government agency, the International Trade Commission, is set to reach a final decision on the new tariffs in June.] https://t.co/wFRD9thI9J - https://t.co/H9WHvWpWBL

💻🇸🇻 El Salvador sedang giat-giatnya mempererat kerjasama dengan Nvidia, perintis dalam teknologi cip komputer, untuk mempercepat pembangunan infrastruktur AI nasional. Langkah ini bertujuan untuk meningkatkan pembangunan ekonomi dan sosial, dengan AI sebagai pendorong utama inovasi. Memandangkan AI menjadi kunci kepada pemodenan teknologi global, El Salvador memposisikan dirinya sebagai salah satu negara yang maju dalam penggunaan teknologi AI secara berdaulat. Jadi, ini bukan hanya kerjasama teknologi semata, tetapi langkah strategik untuk mempertingkat daya saing negara dalam arena global. #AI #ElSalvador

🌐🇫🇷 Minggu Blockchain Paris 2025 menjadi tumpuan utama dunia kripto dengan pengenalan PoSA merge dan blockchain Bahamut. Dengan kehadiran pemenang hackathon dan gesaan kepada penguatkuasaan peraturan aset digital sejagat, peristiwa ini menekankan betapa pentingnya penyesuaian konsensus blokchain yang lebih mapan dan berkesan. Dalam era digital yang kian berubah pantas, Paris menjadi pusat perhatian teknologi blockchain, mencorak masa depan digital yang lebih tegas dan adil. #Blockchain #Paris2025

📈🐋 Sementara Bitcoin terus meroket melebihi $86k, muncul tanda-tanda kebimbangan dalam kalangan ikan paus Bitfinex, yang mula mengurangkan pendedahan leverage mereka. Ini membangkitkan soalan sama ada wujud ketidaktentuan di kalangan pelabur besar tatkala perubahan besar dalam dasar Rizab Persekutuan AS dipertimbangkan. Dengan volatiliti yang tidak menentu, pemegang Bitcoin perlu lebih berhati-hati dan melakukan penilaian risiko secara teliti. #Bitcoin #CryptoVolatility

🌀🔍 Bitget mengalami gelombang penjualan VOXEL yang mencecah $12B, tetapi kejadian ini diikuti dengan pembekuan akaun dan pengembalian dagangan. Kekurangan maklumat terperinci insiden meningkatkan kegusaran mengenai mekanisme perlindungan dan kepercayaan pengguna terhadap platform tersebut. Menghadapi risiko operasi tinggi dalam alam maya, adalah penting bagi platform seperti Bitget untuk meningkatkan ketelusan dan ketahanan sistemnya. #Bitget #Cryptocurrency

📊🚀 Analisis terkini menunjukkan bendera bullish yang jelas pada carta XRP, yang kini berlegar antara $2.12 hingga $2.13. Dengan pengumpulan modal pasaran sebanyak $123 bilion dan volum harian $2.06 bilion, ada harapan bahawa XRP mungkin melangkaui paras psikologi $2.15. Ini mendorong pemain pasaran untuk terus menyokong XRP dalam usaha menawan kembali posisi yang lebih mantap dalam liga altcoin. #XRP #BullishTrend

🔥💬 PlanB sekali lagi melancarkan serangan terhadap Ethereum, mengecam Vitalik Buterin dengan menyatakan bahawa Ethereum adalah 'centralized & premined'. Kritikan ini membangkitkan perdebatan hangat tentang integriti dan pemusatan dalam sistem blokchain, menggariskan jurang pemahaman antara penggemar Bitcoin dan Ethereum. Perselisihan ini mungkin menggugah pelabur untuk mengkaji semula strategi sambil menilai potensi setiap platform secara objektif. #PlanB #Ethereum

🔗💡 Bitcoin yang tidak aktif boleh memberikan potensi besar dalam memacu pertumbuhan dan kestabilan kewangan terdesentralisasi jika digunakan secara bijak. Dengan menjana kecairan tambahan dalam ekosistem DeFi, Bitcoin dapat memperteguh kedudukannya sebagai aset selamat sementara turut menyumbang kepada inovasi kewangan baru. Ini mengangkat makna Bitcoin melebihi sekadar penyimpan nilai kepada pencetus pembaharuan kewangan. #BitcoinDeFi #Innovation

Berbalik kepada realiti, nampaknya kemajuan teknologi ini berjalan laju, tetapi adakah kita semua benar-benar bersedia untuk menghadapinya? Dalam keghairahan mengejar kehebatan teknologi dan perubahan revolusioner, jangan lupa untuk sesaat bertanya: Adakah kita memimpin teknologi, atau adakah teknologi yang memimpin kita? 🤔#TechReflection

Content:
Reflecting on Global AI Bootcamp Kuala Lumpur 2025! 🤖✨

It was fantastic to speak at Microsoft's Global AI Bootcamp KL 2025, held at the Microsoft Malaysia office! Thrilled that nearly 150+ AI enthusiasts joined the session "AI Agents: The Past, Present and Future." 🇲🇾

We explored the exciting world of AI Agents, moving beyond simple automation to systems that perceive, reason, and act autonomously.

Key Takeaways from the Talk: 💡
🧠 What are AI Agents? Intelligent systems that perceive their environment, make decisions, and take actions to achieve goals, adapting and learning along the way. They stand apart from traditional automation due to their ability to analyze, decide, and adapt without constant supervision.

📈 The Agentic Evolution: We've journeyed from rule-based systems in the past decades to the sophisticated, LLM-powered agents emerging today, capable of complex, multi-step tasks and collaboration.

⚙️ Agentic AI Workflows: These AI-driven processes allow agents to manage tasks with minimal human input, adapting to real-time data using components like LLMs, specialized tools, and feedback loops. Different workflow patterns (like chaining, routing, parallelization) enable tackling complex problems.

🛠️ Building the Future: Frameworks like LangChain/LangGraph, AutoGen, CrewAI, Google Vertex AI Agent Builder, and Microsoft Copilot Studio are making it easier to develop these powerful agents. Cognitive architectures like ReAct, Chain of Thought (CoT), and Tree of Thought (ToT) guide how agents reason and solve problems.

🚀 Looking Ahead: The future promises more autonomous, collaborative multi-agent systems deeply integrated into our workflows. Expect hyper-personalized experiences, democratization of services like healthcare 🏥, and significant market growth ($47.1B by 2030!), alongside a crucial focus on ethical development 🤝 and human-AI collaboration.

Thanks to the organizing committee for inviting me🔥
Looking forward to seeing how we all leverage AI agents to build the future. 

#GlobalAIBootcamp #AIagents #ArtificialIntelligence #LLMs #AgenticAI #Microsoft #KualaLumpur #FutureofAI #MachineLearning #Community

Content:
Buzzword Overload Without Substance
Nearly every ministry is claiming "kerjasama" (collaboration), but there's very little detail on what exactly will be done. “AI + China-Malaysia”? Sounds cool… but what does that mean? A chatbot? A lab? A nice signboard?

Where’s the Follow Through?
31 MoUs and documents signed — that’s impressive on paper. But how many of these will actually be implemented? Malaysia has a long tradition of signing MoUs that end up in the filing cabinet of forgotten dreams.

Too Many Ministries, Too Few Results
Every ministry is listed with some kind of collaboration — even Sumber Asli dan Kelestarian Alam (Natural Resources & Environmental Sustainability). But with overlapping responsibilities, how do we measure who’s doing what and whether anything actually improves?
